  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-4b0ba39b-7fff-50e8-01c8-1f742be2f352&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its detailed design, size, massing, and location, would result in overly prominent, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;incongruous, disproportionate, and poorly designed extensions, that would fail to complement the original host building and would have an adverse impact on the wider terrace that the properties are part of. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposal, therefore,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; fails to preserve or enhance the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;character&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; and appearance of the Northwold &amp;amp; Cazenove Conservation Area and would fail to comply with policies D3, D4, and HC1 of The London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 and LP3 of the Hackney Local Plan (2020), and the stipulations of The Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
